00:07:43.279 --> 00:07:44.720
is one of striking the heart,

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:47.639
His Majesty's heart.

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:49.720
And

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.639
the hearts of the court.

